a Cross Heroes]]''\n| Capt. [[John Niel Randle|'Jack' Randle]]\n| Episode: \"The Modern Age\"\n| <ref name=Esquire>{{cite web|author1=Time Lewis |title=How to wear black-tie \u2013 with Tom Hiddleston |url=http://www.esquire.co.uk/style/fashion/1083/how-to-wear-black-tie-with-tom-hiddleston/ |work=[[Esquire (magazine)|Esquire]] |accessdate=17 March 2015 |date=22 November 2011 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150510020524/http://www.esquire.co.uk/style/fashion/1083/how-to-wear-black-tie-with-tom-hiddleston/ |archivedate=10 May 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2006\n| ''[[Suburban Shootout]]''\n| Bill Hazeldine\n| 10 episodes\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Tom Hiddleston Used To Be on a Show Called \"Suburban Shootout\" |url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/ezyeggroll/tom-hiddleston-used-to-be-on-a-show-called-suburba-dha8#.vrp4DOELY |publisher=[[BuzzFeed]] |accessdate=17 March 2015 |date=11 September 2013 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150416043011/http://www.buzzfeed.com/ezyeggroll/tom-hiddleston-used-to-be-on-a-show-called-suburba-dha8 |archivedate=16 April 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2006\n| ''[[Gal\u00e1pagos (2006 TV series)|Gal\u00e1pagos]]''\n| [[Charles Darwin]] (voice)\n| Episode: \"Islands that Changed the World\"\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2007\n| ''[[Casualty (TV series)|Casualty]]''\n| Chris Vaughn\n| Episode: \"The Killing Floor\"\n|\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2008\n| ''[[Wallander (UK TV series)|Wallander]]''\n| Magnus Martinsson\n| 6 episodes\n| <ref>{{cite web|author1=Ben Dowell |title=Kenneth Branagh poised to film the final Wallander series next year |url=http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2014-06-10/kenneth-branagh-poised-to-film-the-final-wallander-series-next-year |publisher=Radio Times |accessdate=17 March 2015 |date=10 June 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318092828/http://www.radiotimes.com/news/2014-06-10/kenneth-branagh-poised-to-film-the-final-wallander-series-next