y-the-hobbit-the-desolation-of-smaug-lead-saturn-awards-noms-1201120744/ |newspaper=Variety |accessdate=14 April 2014 |date=25 February 2014 |title='Gravity,' 'The Hobbit: The Desolation of Smaug' Lead Saturn Awards Noms |first=Nikara |last=Johns |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6Nj6ieckF?url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/gravity-the-hobbit-the-desolation-of-smaug-lead-saturn-awards-noms-1201120744/ |archivedate=28 February 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2014\n| [[Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actor]]\n| ''[[Coriolanus]]''\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite news|last=Denham |first=Jess |title=Olivier Awards 2014: Rory Kinnear beats Jude Law and Tom Hiddleston to Best Actor for Othello |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/theatre-dance/news/olivier-awards-2014-rory-kinnear-crowned-best-actor-for-othello-9257677.html |accessdate=30 May 2014 |newspaper=[[The Independent]] |date=13 April 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140418041221/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/theatre-dance/news/olivier-awards-2014-rory-kinnear-crowned-best-actor-for-othello-9257677.html |archivedate=18 April 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 2014\n| [[Evening Standard Award|Evening Standard Theatre Award for Best Actor]]\n| ''Coriolanus''\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|title=Evening Standard Theatre Awards 2014: Tom Hiddleston and Gillian Anderson take best actor and actress at glittering London awards bash |url=https://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/evening-standard-theatre-awards-2014-tom-hiddleston-and-gillian-anderson-take-best-actor-and-actress-at-glittering-london-awards-bash-9894442.html |work=London Evening Standard |accessdate=1 December 2014 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202173209/http://www.standard.co.uk/showbiz/celebrity-news/evening-standard-theatre-awards-2014-tom-hiddleston-and-gillian-anderson-take-best-actor-and-actress-at-glittering-london-awards-b